Reads recent clips from Twitch channel and posts them to twitter account

Twitch clips gathered are from the past week, in case a user clips something from a VOD.
Clips with !clip or !noclips in the title will be ignored, all others will be gathered.

Clips are gathered at midnight localhost time and are uploaded once every hour between 10 AM and 10 PM localhost time.

Post includes:
- Title
- Clip
Reply includes:
- URL
- Title
- Game
- Clip author
- Clip date

If clips fail to post or gather due to errors (api, internet, unknown), an email is queued and sent to designated email with formatted error message.

Also includes an experimental video converter to make verticle video in the format of Tiktok and Youtube Shorts.